3. cs.CL (Computation and Language) - The paper uses natural language processing techniques to analyze emoticon use in Weibo, which falls under the scope of computation and language.
4. cs.CYBER (Cybersecurity) - The paper touches upon the topic of online marketing, which could potentially involve cybersecurity concerns.
